      "rationale": "Use error assessment not required at MRL 2. Simulation analyst holds relevant CFD credentials and has performed three prior FDA submissions for blood-contacting devices. Peer review of setup files conducted internally."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
