      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 beyond selection rationale documented in simulation report.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for centrifugal blood pump applications. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified at MRL 2; selection rationale documented in simulation plan."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
