      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental sample characterization documented in test report.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood samples prepared per ASTM F1841 with hematocrit 33±2% and age within 48 hours of collection. Sample-to-sample variability not formally propagated into validation uncertainty at MRL 2."
    },
